title: Total United States vehicles entering in Canada 2020
summary: This graph illustrates the Total United States States vehicles to the entering in 2020 .

gold: The chart shows the number of total united states vehicles entering Canada during 2020 . This graph offers an overall downward trend , especially from February to April , with the value shrinking to 1/6 of the previous because of COVID-19 . The number increased steadily from April to June and maintained the same level from June to December .
